title: Dramatic moment London-bound plane intercepted by two fighter jets – as UFO follows
text:
Dramatic moment London-bound plane intercepted by two fighter jets – as UFO follows Dramatic moment London-bound plane intercepted by two fighter jets – as UFO follows THE heart-stopping moment a London-bound airliner was intercepted by two German fighter jets has been caught on camera – with a mysterious UFO following behind.   
Jet Airways flight 9W118 was making its way to London Heathrow from Mumbai, India, when it lost radio contact over Germany. 
Two Eurofighter Typhoons were scrambled by the German Air Force to escort the Boeing 777-300. 
A trailing British Airways plane – soaring 2,000 feet above the Heathrow-bound flight – captured the moment the fighter jets appeared. 
They eventually managed to restore communication, but continued to escort the plane as it made its way into London, according to a Jet Airways statement. 
FACEBOOK BIZARRE: The UFO followed fighter jets as they intercepted a London-bound plane 
But the drama didn’t end there, for some eagle-eyed viewers of the clip. 
Near the end of the video a small black object travelling faster than the other planes is seen – first to the left of the Typhoons, before moving to the top of the screen. 
CirrusPilot – who uploaded the video onto Facebook yesterday (February 19) – wrote: “Many commenters have noted that at the 1min 30sec mark of the video there is a small dark object. 
“The object is moving faster than the other traffic.

“It originates far to the left of the Euro Fighter and takes a 45-degree angle direction towards the North East of the video shot. 
“Perhaps a shadow of another aircraft crossing above.” 
Some sceptical users suggested the object was simply another, smaller, aircraft. Related articles
